ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: ENAS 603 is a course that goes deep into topics relating to transport processes and fluid dynamics. It goes far beyond other courses in examining topics that are widely considered to be active research subjects. I would highly recommend the course for anybody working with fluid flow or combustion.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course provided important physical intuition and understanding of transport processes that are critical in my research/dissertation. The course was invaluable to my work.
